# v2 OOP Refactored Version
## Key Improvements
- Refactored code into object-oriented programming (OOP) structure, splitting into config class, AI logic class, and UI rendering class
- Optimized code modularity to improve maintainability and reusability
- Fine-tuned Streamlit UI layout to enhance user interaction experience
- Separated business logic from interface code, facilitating subsequent function expansion

## Limitations
- Still no exception handling mechanism, insufficient stability
- Knowledge base is still hard-coded in the class, requiring code changes for modifications
- No performance optimization, slow loading of large knowledge bases

## Usage
1. Install dependencies: `pip install -r requirements.txt`
2. Fill in your LLM API key in the config class
3. Run the project: `streamlit run app_v2.py`
